A minimalistic chat server using Node.js
========================================

Found on the web:

    http://dhotson.tumblr.com/post/271733389/a-simple-chat-server-in-node-js

(With little modifications by me)

1. Starting server: 
    
    $ node chat.js

2. Clients can connect with netcat: 

    $ nc localhost 7000

OPTIONS:

    /user  -->  Shows all online users.

    /quit  -->  End the chat appliacation.
